Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.62,0:23:01.49,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}It's just like a burning torch in a storm
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:07.16,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}like a little flower blooming in a home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:12.81,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}強く確かな意思をかかげ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:18.18,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}時に優しくあればいい
